To reduce the canceling of rides:
An amount of 50rs or 100rs as fine for the user, which can redeemed from the user when he/she books his/her next ride.
The amount of the fine can be varied based on time interval between cancellation and Supposed - Pickup time. 
This can help reduce cancellations.

To increase revenue
We can increase the prices for midnight rides and prices for rush hours. 
